          <p>
            <a href="https://www.adlen.nu/" target=”_blank” class="dark-color">Göran Adlén</a>, well-known for his inspiring and
            spot-on trend analysis, talks and books. We work closely with him to keep
            his visuals the same quality, and his new ideas to come
            alive.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="customer-box-item">
          <img src="/img/clients/partners_loggor_eseco_svart.png" alt="" />
          <p>
            <a href="https://www.eseco.se/" target=”_blank” class="dark-color">Eseco</a> in Malmö develops ERP systems making
            e-commerce much easier. XZ is their outsourced marketing department helping them continiously with 
            marketing; social media management, graphic design, marketing
            materials, print and much more.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="customer-box-item">
          <img src="/img/clients/partners_loggor-06.png" alt="" />
